snippet.title: The Making of Turnip Boy Commits Tax Evasion
snippet.description:
Sit down with Yukon, the producer at Snoozy Kazoo, to hear about the process of creating Turnip Boy Commits Tax Evasion from hobby project to fully fledged game. Get some of your burning questions answered, like: How far can they meme? As well as what games influenced Turnip Boy. 


#indiegame #TurnipBoy
